{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以太阳及其光辉发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以追随太阳时的月亮发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以揭示太阳时的白昼发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"以笼罩太阳时的黑夜发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"以苍穹及其建筑者发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"以大地及其铺展者发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"以灵魂及使它均衡，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"并启示他善恶者发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"凡培养自己的性灵者，必定成功；"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"凡戕害自己的性灵者，必定失败。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"赛莫德人已因过分而否认真理。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"当时，他们中最薄命者忙上前来，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"使者就对他们说：“你们让安拉的母驼自由饮水吧。”"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"但他们否认使者而宰杀母驼，故他们的主因他们的罪过而毁灭他们，使他们普遍受难。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他是不顾虑那灾难的后果的。"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以笼罩时的黑夜发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以显著时的白昼发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以创造男性和女性的主发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"你们的行为，确是不同的。"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"至于赈济贫民，敬畏安拉，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"且承认至善者，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"我将使他易于达到最易的结局。"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"至于吝惜钱财，自谓无求，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"且否认至善者，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"我将使他易于达到最难的结局。"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"当他沦亡的时候，他的财产于他有什么裨益呢！"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"我确有指导的责任，"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"我确有后世和今世的主权。"},{"SurahNumber":92,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"故我警告你们一种发焰的火，"}]}